name: James Hickey
what_you_do: Jim Hickey provides online coaching and membership programs to help riders overcome challenges and improve their mindset and confidence in the ring.
who_you_serve: Riders of all levels, from beginners to Olympic-level competitors.
signature_programs: The Jim Hickey Online Coaching Membership, which includes 12 coaching courses on topics like rebuilding confidence, overcoming panic and anxiety, and becoming fearless on show day.
business_focus: Providing online coaching and membership programs to help equestrian riders improve their mental game and performance in the ring.
